<!DOCTYPE html><html ⚡><head> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-head.ejs %><link rel="canonical" href="/Quick-Installation/How_Does_An_IP_Camera_Work"></head><body class="home"> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-header.ejs %><div class="wrap"><div class="container main"> <% include ../_partials/content/_bluenav-qi.ejs %><article class="content"><div class="margin"><table><tr><td><h1 class="inlineHeader">Quick Installation Wizard&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</h1></td><td> <a href="http://install.instar.de" target="_blank"><button class="navGoRed">Get Started</button></a></td></tr></table></div><div class="margin"><amp-youtube data-videoid="ByMkfVgjl3c" layout="responsive" width="480" height="270" class="shadow"></amp-youtube></div><div class="margin"><h1>First Steps</h1><p class="text-justify">This video contains a quick overview over the first steps involved in setting up your IP camera. Please go to the website <a href="http://install.instar.de">Installation Wizard</a> and follow the step by step instructions in order to set up your ip camera. Your will have your camera connected to your LAN or WiFi network in no-time. The following steps will help you to get access to the more advanced features of your camera.<br/><br/></p><ul><li>Check out our <a href="/Quick_Installation/After_Unpacking">After Unpacking</a> guide.<br/><br/></li><li>All camera functions are accessible through the <strong>web user interface</strong>. Click here to access the user guide for the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/">1080p Series</a> or <a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/">720p Series</a> Web UI. You can change the language of the UI <a href="/Quick_Installation/Language_Selection">here</a>.<br/><br/></li><li>If you cannot access your camera´s <strong>live video stream</strong>, take a look <a href="/Quick_Installation/Live_Video">here</a>.<br/><br/></li><li>The installation wizard already guided you through the generation of an administrator user. If you want to <strong>change your login</strong>, or add user or visitor accounts, click <a href="/Quick_Installation/Creating_User_Accounts">here</a>.<br/><br/></li><li>It is always <strong>recommended to update</strong> your camera´s web user interface and firmware before you start using it. Get information about updates <a href="/Quick_Installation/WebUI_And_Firmware_Upgrade">here</a>.<br/><br/></li><li>You want to have full access to your camera when on the road? Learn everything about our <a href="/Internet_Access/The_DDNS_Service">DDNS Servcie</a> and how to set a <a href="/Internet_Access/Port_Forwarding">Port Forwarding</a> inside your router.<br/><br/></li><li>Set up the <a href="/Motion_Detection/Setup">Motion Detection</a> and <a href="/Motion_Detection/Alarm_Notification">Alarm Notification</a>.</li></ul></div></article></div></div> <% include ../_partials/content/_bluenav-qi-mobile.ejs %><footer> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-footer.ejs %></footer></body></html>